fields.name: Vintage T Plus Series electric guitar
fields.title: Vintage "T" Plus Series electric guitar
fields.description:
- Body: Solid paulownia 
- Neck: Maple, satin finish, bolt-on with easy access to the last frets
- Scale: 648mm, (25.5")
- Fingerboard: Maple, 22 frets 
- Pickups: 1 x single coil + 1 x humbucker 
- Controls: 1 x volume with push-pull to split humbucker + 1 x tone 
- Pickup selector switch: 3-way 
- Bridge: "T" style, strings through body 
- Machine heads: Diecast, nickel 
- Nut: Bone 
- Strings: made in Korea
- Finish: Highgloss

- Volume control
- Compression control
- Headphone output

fields.name: 20-watt spring reverb acoustic amplifier
fields.title: 20-watt spring reverb acoustic amplifier
fields.description:
- Power: 20 watts (RMS)
- Speaker: 8", 4 ohms, with coaxial tweeter
- Frequency response: 70 Hz - 12 kHz
- Total harmonic distortion: 0.2 %
- Signal to noise ratio: -64 dB at maximum rated power
- Input impedance: 200k ohms (instrument)
- Controls: 3-band equaliser (bass, middle, treble) with parametric mid, active or passive instrument mode
- Inputs: Instrument, microphone, auxiliary device (stereo jack)
- Output: Headphones (6.35 mm (1/4") standard jack)
- Feature: Versatile spring reverb
- Power consumption: 56 watts maximum 
- Dimensions: 40.3 x 34.7 x 19.4 cm (15.9 x 13.7 x 7.6")
- Weight: 8.5 kg (18.7 lb)
